body_html:
@gunan Heads up: this is the second recent bug I've seen where someone somehow got an empty installation of TensorFlow (no tf.constant here, no tf.Variable for #7285). This one is anaconda; not sure about the other one yet.

@danchokobo We don't support Anaconda, so if you installed it through that you should look at Anaconda docs to know how to uninstall.

@gunan Heads up: this is the second recent bug I've seen where someone somehow got an empty installation of TensorFlow (no `tf.constant` here, no `tf.Variable` for https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/7285).  This one is anaconda; not sure about the other one yet.

@danchokobo We don't support Anaconda, so if you installed it through that you should look at Anaconda docs to know how to uninstall.
